## Rollback Plan

If migration fails:

### Quick Rollback (Before Production)
```bash
# In staging, revert to previous provider
git revert <commit>
pnpm install  # Restores old dependencies
pnpm run dev
```

### Production Rollback
```bash
# 1. Keep both providers running during migration
# 2. Monitor error rates and user reports
# 3. If critical issues:
#    a. Switch traffic to old provider
#    b. Revert environment variables
#    c. Restore database backup if needed
#    d. Notify affected users
```

